  <div class="container mx-auto p-4">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">About Page</h1>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Data Sources</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mb-4">
      <li class="mb-4">
        <strong>Recreation Complexes:</strong> Data sourced from <a href="https://data.winnipeg.ca/Recreation/Recreation-Complex/bmi4-vvs2/about_data" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Winnipeg's recreation complex dataset</a>. This dataset provides information about various recreation complexes in Winnipeg. It includes details such as the name of the complex.
      </li>
      <li class="mb-4">
        <strong>Libraries:</strong> Data obtained from <a href="https://data.winnipeg.ca/Libraries/Library/bt47-pkkm/about_data" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Winnipeg's library dataset</a>. This table will store information about libraries, including their names, locations, amenities, and services offered. Each library is associated with a recreation complex by the recreation_complex_id column.
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Description:</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
      The recreation_complex table contains information about various recreational facilities in Winnipeg. The library table includes information about library locations, their amenities, and the services they offer. Each library is associated with a recreation complex via the recreation_complex_id column, establishing a one-to-one relationship where a single recreation complex with a single library is associated with it.
    </p>

